486
00:15:09.784 --> 00:15:12.704
I think. like. 20 million people
die like that every month.

487
00:15:12.704 --> 00:15:14.664
What? Oh. my God.
that's so many.

488
00:15:14.664 --> 00:15:16.708
That's awful.
Wait. it can't be that many.

489
00:15:16.708 --> 00:15:18.043
Just stay away from the oven.

490
00:15:18.043 --> 00:15:19.753
You know what? I'm calling
