491
00:15:19.753 --> 00:15:22.672
Fine. call him.
but try not be how you are.

492
00:15:22.672 --> 00:15:24.132
I always try to do that.

493
00:15:24.132 --> 00:15:26.926
(sighs) Bob sounded
so upset in that message.

494
00:15:26.926 --> 00:15:30.013
He just had to razz.
and now his family's freezing.

495
00:15:30.013 --> 00:15:32.349
That's straight. right?
Looks straight.

496
00:15:32.349 --> 00:15:34.601
What does it even matter?
People are dying out there.

497
00:15:34.601 --> 00:15:36.061
MAN:
You doing okay?

498
00:15:36.061 --> 00:15:37.729
Yes. I'm fine. Mr. Yazdian.

499
00:15:37.729 --> 00:15:39.064
Everything's fine!

500
00:15:39.064 --> 00:15:40.648
Tina. it's really cold

501
00:15:40.648 --> 00:15:42.150
and windy and snowy out there.

502
00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:43.818
The truth will keep me warm.

503
00:15:43.818 --> 00:15:45.487
I mean. it's like
really cold. Tina.

504
00:15:45.487 --> 00:15:48.239
Justice will be my jacket.
And also this jacket.

505
00:15:48.239 --> 00:15:50.241
Mm-hmm. And what do we
tell Mom and Dad

506
00:15:50.241 --> 00:15:51.242
