556
00:17:19.080 --> 00:17:21.416
That's Billy's business.
So. back off.

557
00:17:21.416 --> 00:17:23.752
No. I'm gonna tell
Mr. Frond I'm not a cheater.

558
00:17:23.752 --> 00:17:26.546
Oh. I don't know. Tina.
I mean. is that true?

559
00:17:26.546 --> 00:17:27.547
Yes. it's true.

560
00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:29.424
Okay. But. like. uh.
I have to ask...

561
00:17:29.424 --> 00:17:30.842
What would you have done
if Susmita had

562
00:17:30.842 --> 00:17:32.635
