- What?

563
00:17:32.635 --> 00:17:34.804
When you looked at her test.
she had the same answer.

564
00:17:34.804 --> 00:17:36.556
But what if she had
circled a different answer?

565
00:17:36.556 --> 00:17:38.475
What would you have done?
Would you have changed yours?

566
00:17:38.475 --> 00:17:40.977
No. I-I mean...
I don't want to talk about it.

567
00:17:40.977 --> 00:17:42.437
Tina. you can tell me.

568
00:17:42.437 --> 00:17:44.606
In fact. you should tell me.
It'll feel better.

569
00:17:44.606 --> 00:17:45.648
And if you don't tell me.

570
00:17:45.648 --> 00:17:47.025
it'll make Billy angry.

571
00:17:47.025 --> 00:17:48.610
And you don't
want to make Billy angry.

572
00:17:48.610 --> 00:17:50.070
<i>Da-da-da-dah ♪</i>

573
00:17:50.070 --> 00:17:52.739
Whoa. Okay. maybe
I would've cheated.

574
00:17:52.739 --> 00:17:54.699
Okay. Billy?
If she had a different answer.

575
00:17:54.699 --> 00:17:56.284
maybe I would've
changed mine to hers.

576
00:17:56.284 --> 00:17:57.494
I studied so hard for that test

577
00:17:57.494 --> 00:17:59.037
and I wanted
to get a good grade.

578
00:17:59.037 --> 00:18:00.497
So. I guess
maybe I am a cheater.

579
00:18:00.497 --> 00:18:01.581
Are you happy? Huh?

580
00:18:01.581 --> 00:18:02.624
I mean. a little.

581
00:18:02.624 --> 00:18:03.875
{\an8}Ugh. God. (grunts)

582
00:18:03.875 --> 00:18:05.460
{\an8}Uh. no. don't kick snow at me.

583
00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:07.170
{\an8}I'll kick snow at you. (grunts)

584
00:18:07.170 --> 00:18:08.880
{\an8}(both grunting)

585
00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:09.881
