Tina?

586
00:18:09.881 --> 00:18:11.091
- Is that you?
- Teddy?

587
00:18:11.091 --> 00:18:12.092
What are you doing out here?

588
00:18:12.092 --> 00:18:13.885
Were you screaming
and kicking snow?

589
00:18:13.885 --> 00:18:15.637
Uh. a little. Yeah.

590
00:18:15.637 --> 00:18:16.971
Y-Your dad said he upset

591
00:18:16.971 --> 00:18:19.307
the heater repair guy
and he's not gonna come.

592
00:18:19.307 --> 00:18:21.059
I finished the
other job really well.

593
00:18:21.059 --> 00:18:23.478
