so I decided to walk.

595
00:18:25.939 --> 00:18:26.940
Get on my back.

596
00:18:26.940 --> 00:18:28.608
I mean. I can probably walk.

597
00:18:28.608 --> 00:18:30.485
Okay. good. Thanks.

598
00:18:30.485 --> 00:18:31.695
The tools are kind of heavy.

599
00:18:31.695 --> 00:18:33.363
- I'm gonna go find Tina.
- (front door opens)

600
00:18:33.363 --> 00:18:34.614
Never mind. Tina's here.

601
00:18:34.614 --> 00:18:35.907
With Teddy.

602
00:18:35.907 --> 00:18:37.158
Don't worry. you're all safe.

603
00:18:37.158 --> 00:18:38.576
Teddy's here to save the day.

604
00:18:38.576 --> 00:18:40.745
I'm gonna fix your heater.
But I'm also really cold.

605
00:18:40.745 --> 00:18:42.706
And weak.
And I can't feel my body.

606
00:18:42.706 --> 00:18:44.249
But then Chelsea told on me

607
00:18:44.249 --> 00:18:45.542
that I was a cheater.
and maybe I am a cheater

608
00:18:45.542 --> 00:18:47.377
'cause if Susmita had
had a different answer.

609
00:18:47.377 --> 00:18:49.546
I might have changed mine
like a cheating cheater.

610
00:18:49.546 --> 00:18:50.964
So this is why you've been

611
00:18:50.964 --> 00:18:53.008
