moping around.

612
00:18:53.008 --> 00:18:55.969
Destroying award-winning pillow
and blanket architecture.

613
00:18:55.969 --> 00:18:57.387
I'm a terrible cheater person.

614
00:18:57.387 --> 00:18:59.097
You're not a terrible
cheater person.

615
00:18:59.097 --> 00:19:01.182
You didn't cheat.
so let's start there.

616
00:19:01.182 --> 00:19:03.393
Maybe if Susmita
had a different answer.

617
00:19:03.393 --> 00:19:05.520
